Physical effect diagram
Traditional packaging boxes are mostly made of tin, paper, or plastic. Although these types of packaging can effectively protect the product, they cannot immediately showcase the product's appearance and features. 
They also fail to meet the requirements for creating differentiated packaging and enhancing product marketing effectiveness. Transparent packaging boxes, on the other hand, not only allow consumers to see and understand the product at first glance but also boost their purchasing power.
src: 传统的包装盒多为铁盒，纸盒，塑料等包装，虽然这类包装盒也能很好的保护产品，但他们都不能第一时间的展现产品的外观和特点，更不能满足打造差异化包装和提升产品营销效果的要求，而透明包装盒除了可以让消费者第一时间看到产品，了解产品，还能提升消费者购买力。
